title: Gluten Free Carrot and Date Muffins
ingredients: ['120g white rice flour', '120g brown rice flour', '1 teaspoon xanthan gum', '2 teaspoons gluten free baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon gluten free bicarbonate of soda', '1/2 teaspoon fine salt', '2 organic eggs', '125ml soya milk', '60ml organic grapeseed oil', '150g honey', '2 medium carrots, finely grated', '170g chopped dates']
